                    Your Tax Filing Status determines which <a href="http://taxfoundation.org/article/2016-tax-brackets">tax brackets</a> apply to you.  
                  </p>
                  <p>
                    Most people will be paying significantly less, or even no, taxes in retirement.  
                    To estimate your budget for your current lifestyle, this calculator subtracts out estimated Federal taxes from your income.
                  </p>
